<h2>Troubleshooting</h2>

<h3>1. Common Issues</h3>
<ul>
<li><strong>Theme not loading</strong>: Check file permissions and path configuration</li>
<li><strong>Changes not saving</strong>: Verify write permissions on theme directory</li>
<li><strong>Preview not updating</strong>: Clear browser cache and reload editor</li>
</ul>

<h3>2. Log Locations</h3>
<ul>
<li>Application logs: <code>/Comserv/logs/application.log</code></li>
<li>Theme-specific logs: Check controller logging output</li>
<li>JavaScript errors: Browser developer console</li>
</ul>

